# React Best Practices

## Project Context

TREND Hair Boutique Studio website -- luxury hairdressing salon with baroque-inspired design, bilingual support (EN/BG), Three.js animations on desktop, deployed to GitHub Pages.

## Core Principles

- Functional components with hooks only
- Extract reusable logic into custom hooks
- Named exports for components
- Keep components under 200 lines

## SEO

Every page must call `usePageSEO({ title, description })` with values from `translations.seo`. New pages require adding SEO keys to translations.

## Pricing

Display EUR only. Do not show BGN or dual currency.

